        "timestamp": "2017-08-01 13:26:14.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nI am a bit uncomfortable with the use of pieces dependent on our specific environment. The namespace name and the name search patch of our kubernetes cluster which is for us svc.cluster.local. But I think this is a trade-off we have to allow until we introduce a way to parameterize that. \nRegarding the patch related to hbase, I would only go with the kubernetes manifest change and let hbase try to create the directory structure by himself.",
